00:15:20,320 --> 00:15:21,500
send the case back

285
00:15:21,600 --> 00:15:23,500
and let them handle it internally.

286
00:15:23,760 --> 00:15:26,420
The commissioner chewed me out:

287
00:15:27,200 --> 00:15:27,780
"Hong Liang,

288
00:15:28,320 --> 00:15:29,660
have you forgotten

289
00:15:29,680 --> 00:15:31,620
the Eleventh Division's

290
00:15:31,640 --> 00:15:32,460
mandate?

291
00:15:32,480 --> 00:15:33,580
What were you thinking?"

292
00:15:34,000 --> 00:15:35,100
I was mortified.

293
00:15:35,720 --> 00:15:36,540
But actually,

294
00:15:36,640 --> 00:15:38,020
he's right.

295
00:15:38,440 --> 00:15:39,300
Mr. Wang

296
00:15:39,880 --> 00:15:41,380
is on secondment from Jiangnan

297
00:15:41,760 --> 00:15:43,260
to the provincial office,

298
00:15:44,040 --> 00:15:45,780
and the incident happened

299
00:15:45,800 --> 00:15:48,100
while he was working for us.

300
00:15:49,360 --> 00:15:50,100
Well,

301
00:15:51,600 --> 00:15:53,260
you processed

302
00:15:53,520 --> 00:15:55,060
that secondment,

303
00:15:55,280 --> 00:15:57,580
so you know the details
better than I do.

304
00:15:57,600 --> 00:15:58,820
Don't make this hard on me.

305
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:08,380
Hong Liang,

306
00:16:10,720 --> 00:16:11,260
look,

307
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:13,020
our work should balance

308
00:16:13,960 --> 00:16:15,940
moral principle, state law
and human feeling.

309
00:16:16,240 --> 00:16:17,540
Your Eleventh Division

310
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:18,740
respects principle

311
00:16:19,280 --> 00:16:19,820
and law,

312
00:16:20,720 --> 00:16:21,900
but do you respect human feeling?

313
00:16:29,400 --> 00:16:29,900
Hello?

314
00:16:30,040 --> 00:16:31,300
Hong Liang,
stop pretending to take a call.

315
00:16:35,320 --> 00:16:35,700
Hong,

316
00:16:36,360 --> 00:16:37,140
are you free right now?

317
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:39,340
Hello?

318
00:16:39,880 --> 00:16:40,220
Hello?

319
00:16:41,160 --> 00:16:41,580
Hong,

320
00:16:42,200 --> 00:16:43,060
can you hear me?

321
00:16:43,080 --> 00:16:44,740
I can hear you. Go ahead.

322
00:16:44,880 --> 00:16:45,340
Hong?

323
00:16:46,400 --> 00:16:46,860
Hong?

324
00:16:47,400 --> 00:16:48,260
- Hello?
- Can you hear me?

325
00:16:53,560 --> 00:16:54,020
Finished with your call?

326
00:16:55,480 --> 00:16:56,140
Please continue.

327
00:16:56,880 --> 00:16:57,620
Answer me:

328
00:16:57,960 --> 00:16:59,420
does the Eleventh Division

329
00:17:00,440 --> 00:17:01,580
take human feeling into account?

330
00:17:09,920 --> 00:17:11,500
The law restrains citizens,

331
00:17:12,720 --> 00:17:13,500
and law-enforcers

332
00:17:13,680 --> 00:17:15,180
must be restrained by the law even more.

333
00:17:16,040 --> 00:17:17,820
Only then can justice stay fair.

334
00:17:18,760 --> 00:17:20,340
The Eleventh Division exists

335
00:17:20,720 --> 00:17:22,100
to turn the blade inward

336
00:17:22,360 --> 00:17:23,460
and police our own.

337
00:17:23,840 --> 00:17:25,380
I believe you understand

338
00:17:25,720 --> 00:17:27,780
our purpose better than I do.

339
00:17:28,400 --> 00:17:29,940
If you think

340
00:17:29,960 --> 00:17:31,460
today's methods are improper,

341
00:17:31,480 --> 00:17:33,140
feel free to report us to the leadership.

342
00:17:33,160 --> 00:17:34,420
I'll accept any criticism.

343
00:17:34,680 --> 00:17:35,540
If you believe

344
00:17:35,560 --> 00:17:37,260
our disciplinary recommendation

345
00:17:37,520 --> 00:17:39,860
exceeds the rules,

346
00:17:40,120 --> 00:17:42,820
you're welcome to appeal
through the proper channels.

347
00:17:42,880 --> 00:17:43,700
I will appeal.

348
00:17:43,720 --> 00:17:44,060
Fine.

349
00:17:44,840 --> 00:17:45,980
Then give me the time to do it.

350
00:17:46,200 --> 00:17:47,020
Certainly, Ms. Zheng.

351
00:17:47,320 --> 00:17:47,860
Zhang,

352
00:17:48,280 --> 00:17:49,300
Mr. Wang doesn't need

353
00:17:49,840 --> 00:17:50,980
to sign today.

354
00:17:51,560 --> 00:17:52,260
But Ms. Zheng,

355
00:17:52,280 --> 00:17:53,980
please give me a written statement

356
00:17:54,120 --> 00:17:55,420
explaining why our investigation

357
00:17:55,600 --> 00:17:56,980
was interrupted.

358
00:17:57,280 --> 00:17:58,460
Otherwise I have nothing to report.

359
00:18:02,680 --> 00:18:03,260
I signed it.

360
00:18:05,120 --> 00:18:05,660
Sorry for the trouble.

361
00:18:10,520 --> 00:18:18,680
[Dongping, Haidong Province]

362
00:18:20,400 --> 00:18:22,520
[Dongping Municipal Committee of CPC]

363
00:18:22,520 --> 00:18:23,740
We're holding an ad-hoc meeting today.

364
00:18:24,080 --> 00:18:25,820
President Liu at the court
is still in the hospital,

365
00:18:26,800 --> 00:18:28,020
so Chief Judge Wen
is standing in for him.

366
00:18:29,440 --> 00:18:33,440
[Lan Jingming, Secretary,
Political and Legal Affairs Commission]

367
00:18:41,280 --> 00:18:42,340
This case has dragged on

368
00:18:43,720 --> 00:18:44,340
for more than two years,

369
00:18:45,280 --> 00:18:46,340
and everyone here

370
00:18:47,320 --> 00:18:48,700
has put in real effort.

371
00:18:49,160 --> 00:18:50,420
What happened today

372
00:18:51,680 --> 00:18:52,460
is on us,

373
00:18:53,480 --> 00:18:54,140
so let me start with self-criticism:

374
00:18:55,080 --> 00:18:56,540
our pre-trial review

375
00:18:57,680 --> 00:18:58,500
wasn't thorough,

376
00:18:59,480 --> 00:19:00,460
and the prosecution team

377
00:19:01,960 --> 00:19:04,100
failed to spot Zhang Wenjing's

378
00:19:04,520 --> 00:19:04,980
unstable state of mind,

379
00:19:05,400 --> 00:19:06,780
causing trouble for the rest of you.

380
00:19:06,800 --> 00:19:07,300
Enough.

381
00:19:09,200 --> 00:19:10,300
There'll be time for self-reflection.

382
00:19:12,440 --> 00:19:13,740
Director Xu, give us the essentials.

383
00:19:14,360 --> 00:19:15,520
[Xu Yanwu
Director, Dongping Public Security Bureau]

384
00:19:15,520 --> 00:19:17,740
Secretary Lan, I'll keep it brief.

385
00:19:18,880 --> 00:19:21,860
It's a fact that Zhang Wenjing
intimidated witnesses

386
00:19:22,520 --> 00:19:23,780
and forged testimony.

387
00:19:24,840 --> 00:19:26,100
We have solid proof,

388
00:19:26,800 --> 00:19:28,500
including witness statements
and physical proof

389
00:19:29,080 --> 00:19:30,860
that corroborate each other.

390
00:19:31,560 --> 00:19:32,860
As for

391
00:19:32,920 --> 00:19:34,500
what exactly happened to her

392
00:19:34,880 --> 00:19:36,100
during the review phase,

393
00:19:37,400 --> 00:19:37,940
well...

394
00:19:45,840 --> 00:19:47,600
[Wen Qin
Chief Judge, First Criminal Division]

395
00:19:47,600 --> 00:19:48,580
Given the gravity

396
00:19:49,320 --> 00:19:50,100
of this case,

397
00:19:50,880 --> 00:19:51,660
the panel

398
00:19:52,080 --> 00:19:55,260
studied the file in depth before trial,

399
00:19:55,720 --> 00:19:57,900
vetted every piece
of evidence and document,

400
00:19:58,440 --> 00:20:01,300
did special research
on the tough issues,

401
00:20:01,680 --> 00:20:03,460
and only opened court
once everything checked out.

402
00:20:06,360 --> 00:20:07,020
Zhang Wenjing

403
00:20:07,960 --> 00:20:09,380
is Wan Group's legal director

404
00:20:09,920 --> 00:20:12,060
and has been acting
as Wan Hai's defense counsel

405
00:20:12,960 --> 00:20:14,300
since his detention.

406
00:20:15,720 --> 00:20:16,420
As for the details,

407
00:20:16,520 --> 00:20:16,940
Mr. Xie,

408
00:20:17,720 --> 00:20:18,340
you can do the introduction.

409
00:20:19,160 --> 00:20:19,460
Right.

410
00:20:20,120 --> 00:20:21,660
During the review,

411
00:20:21,960 --> 00:20:22,940
we found

412
00:20:23,320 --> 00:20:23,940
she knew full well

413
00:20:24,320 --> 00:20:27,060
the gang was committing crimes

414
00:20:27,360 --> 00:20:29,980
yet kept providing legal assistance.

415
00:20:30,640 --> 00:20:31,540
Digging further,

416
00:20:31,880 --> 00:20:32,900
we discovered

417
00:20:32,920 --> 00:20:35,180
she'd already

418
00:20:35,720 --> 00:20:37,660
taken part in

419
00:20:37,920 --> 00:20:39,340
multiple fraud and extortion cases

420
00:20:39,440 --> 00:20:40,980
for the gang over the years.

421
00:20:41,400 --> 00:20:42,100
In short,

422
00:20:42,320 --> 00:20:44,940
she's a core member.

423
00:21:13,400 --> 00:21:15,120
[Fu Bing
Defence Counsel for Zhang Wenjing]

424
00:21:15,120 --> 00:21:16,220
What's with you?

425
00:21:16,960 --> 00:21:18,780
If you planned to speak out like that,

426
00:21:18,960 --> 00:21:20,860
shouldn't you have told me first?

427
00:21:33,360 --> 00:21:35,340
At least give me a heads-up

428
00:21:36,120 --> 00:21:37,140
so I can prepare

429
00:21:37,240 --> 00:21:38,660
and make it land better.

430
00:21:39,120 --> 00:21:39,940
Walls have ears.

431
00:21:41,400 --> 00:21:42,940
I'm the only one who can know,

432
00:21:43,840 --> 00:21:45,300
and I only got one chance to speak.

433
00:21:57,200 --> 00:21:57,900
So what's the next move?

434
00:22:01,120 --> 00:22:01,540
Never mind,

435
00:22:02,120 --> 00:22:02,580
don't say.

436
00:22:04,760 --> 00:22:05,220
Relax,

437
00:22:06,040 --> 00:22:07,340
I'll use every contact I have

438
00:22:07,480 --> 00:22:09,260
to find out

439
00:22:09,680 --> 00:22:11,300
how the higher-ups really view this.

440
00:22:11,920 --> 00:22:12,860
I'll sound out

441
00:22:13,440 --> 00:22:13,900
the bar association too.

442
00:22:14,760 --> 00:22:16,380
You've stirred things up so much

443
00:22:16,600 --> 00:22:17,380
that we need

444
00:22:18,000 --> 00:22:19,180
some sign of what's coming,

445
00:22:20,040 --> 00:22:20,460
right?

446
00:22:25,520 --> 00:22:26,740
I asked for a post-mortem

447
00:22:27,120 --> 00:22:28,540
and all I hear

448
00:22:28,640 --> 00:22:29,940
is how hard

449
00:22:30,360 --> 00:22:31,620
you worked.

450
00:22:32,280 --> 00:22:33,660
Two and a half years,

451
00:22:34,240 --> 00:22:35,660
and day one of trial

452
00:22:36,200 --> 00:22:37,780
turns into this.

453
00:22:39,480 --> 00:22:40,940
Renjun called to tell me

454
00:22:41,840 --> 00:22:43,460
to "watch public opinion".

455
00:22:44,640 --> 00:22:45,220
Tell me,

456
00:22:45,640 --> 00:22:47,660
is merely "watching" enough?

457
00:22:48,560 --> 00:22:50,980
As the acting prosecutor-general,

458
00:22:51,960 --> 00:22:53,220
what are your responsibilities?

459
00:22:53,720 --> 00:22:55,420
What are your top priorities?

460
00:22:55,840 --> 00:22:57,820
I'm not criticizing the prosecution

461
00:22:57,920 --> 00:22:58,940
just because
I came up through its ranks.

462
00:23:01,200 --> 00:23:02,780
I'm asking what case review
and indictment are for.

463
00:23:03,440 --> 00:23:05,020
Isn't the whole point
to get ready for trial?

464
00:23:05,520 --> 00:23:06,340
If your work

465
00:23:06,360 --> 00:23:07,620
had been solid,

466
00:23:08,560 --> 00:23:10,460
would Zhang Wenjing's outburst
have happened?

467
00:23:20,760 --> 00:23:22,340
Stop passing the buck

468
00:23:22,600 --> 00:23:23,940
and stop dodging the real issues.

469
00:23:24,560 --> 00:23:26,340
The problem lies with the prosecution.

470
00:23:26,880 --> 00:23:28,700
Public Security
must dig deeper into the facts.

471
00:23:28,960 --> 00:23:29,300
Understood.

472
00:23:29,800 --> 00:23:31,740
The procuratorate needs
to tighten its review,

473
00:23:32,000 --> 00:23:33,700
make the evidence rock-solid.

474
00:23:34,160 --> 00:23:35,100
Once it's solid,

475
00:23:35,720 --> 00:23:36,900
her plea

476
00:23:37,840 --> 00:23:39,260
won't affect the verdict.

477
00:23:39,720 --> 00:23:40,860
We'll draft a plan as soon as possible.

478
00:23:43,600 --> 00:23:49,680
[Dongping No. 2 Detention Center
Haidong Province]

479
00:24:00,520 --> 00:24:00,900
Thanks.

480
00:24:09,600 --> 00:24:09,980
Thank you.

481
00:24:32,960 --> 00:24:36,520
[Cheng Zijian
Defence Counsel for Wan Hai]

482
00:24:56,720 --> 00:24:59,860
Zhang said in court I'm not mafia.

483
00:25:01,200 --> 00:25:01,940
What do you make of that?

484
00:25:03,320 --> 00:25:04,220
How am I supposed to take it?

485
00:25:05,800 --> 00:25:06,620
I'm asking you:

486
00:25:08,720 --> 00:25:09,860
am I mafia?

487
00:25:11,000 --> 00:25:11,660
What's that supposed to mean?

488
00:25:13,520 --> 00:25:14,740
I'm asking you:

489
00:25:16,240 --> 00:25:17,940
am I mafia?

490
00:25:27,600 --> 00:25:28,260
Aren't you?

491
00:25:33,680 --> 00:25:35,820
Quit buzzing in my ear.

492
00:25:36,280 --> 00:25:38,180
You can't even handle Zhang Wenjing.

493
00:25:39,040 --> 00:25:40,500
Aren't you all so capable?

494
00:25:41,000 --> 00:25:43,620
Tell me when the next hearing is.

495
00:25:44,480 --> 00:25:45,380
You screwed up!

496
00:25:56,800 --> 00:25:57,780
Zhang Wenjing.

497
00:26:01,280 --> 00:26:03,340
Her antics

498
00:26:03,960 --> 00:26:04,580
won't change

499
00:26:04,600 --> 00:26:06,900
the fact she's a core member

500
00:26:06,920 --> 00:26:07,820
of a

501
00:26:08,800 --> 00:26:09,460
criminal gang.

502
00:26:10,680 --> 00:26:13,340
I'm sure the next session will be soon,

503
00:26:14,240 --> 00:26:15,660
and the outcome I promised,

504
00:26:16,160 --> 00:26:16,900
sentence reduction

505
00:26:17,920 --> 00:26:18,820
for meritorious service,

506
00:26:19,680 --> 00:26:21,300
will still go ahead.

507
00:26:23,520 --> 00:26:26,060
You have to trust me now.

508
00:26:35,280 --> 00:26:37,020
I said everyone had to be here.

509
00:26:37,480 --> 00:26:38,580
Why isn't Mr. Qiao?

510
00:26:40,000 --> 00:26:41,580
Two years ago this was his case.

511
00:26:42,920 --> 00:26:43,740
We called him.

512
00:26:44,280 --> 00:26:45,500
I even saw him this morning,

513
00:26:46,160 --> 00:26:47,260
but he's gone dark since.

514
00:26:48,080 --> 00:26:49,220
This is the team you're leading?

515
00:26:50,360 --> 00:26:51,340
The provincial leadership

516
00:26:51,440 --> 00:26:52,740
probably already knows
about Zhang Wenjing.

517
00:26:53,680 --> 00:26:54,700
Don't wait for them to ask,

518
00:26:55,240 --> 00:26:56,180
report first.

519
00:26:57,960 --> 00:26:58,700
Figure out fast

520
00:26:59,480 --> 00:27:00,180
how you're going to frame it.

521
00:27:03,120 --> 00:27:03,740
What about my son?

522
00:27:04,680 --> 00:27:06,500
Why was he in court?

523
00:27:07,240 --> 00:27:08,980
Why is he even in Dongping?

524
00:27:09,800 --> 00:27:11,220
What did you promise me?

525
00:27:11,600 --> 00:27:13,540
Who said they'd ship him overseas?

526
00:27:14,040 --> 00:27:15,020
Let me tell you:

527
00:27:17,160 --> 00:27:19,380
if anything happens to that boy,

528
00:27:20,160 --> 00:27:22,020
none of you can walk away clean.

529
00:27:25,200 --> 00:27:27,260
Do you know how many times
I tried to talk him down?

530
00:27:28,320 --> 00:27:30,740
He's just as stubborn as you.

531
00:27:31,280 --> 00:27:32,660
He turned up in court

532
00:27:33,160 --> 00:27:35,100
because he knew the date,

533
00:27:35,520 --> 00:27:36,860
and he's still in Dongping

534
00:27:37,040 --> 00:27:38,500
because I couldn't budge him.

535
00:27:39,280 --> 00:27:39,980
I'm telling you,

536
00:27:40,320 --> 00:27:42,740
today he disrupted proceedings.

537
00:27:43,080 --> 00:27:45,060
If I hadn't stepped in
he'd already be detained.

538
00:27:51,440 --> 00:27:53,100
Send him a message.

539
00:27:53,680 --> 00:27:54,620
You tell him:

540
00:27:55,480 --> 00:27:57,540
I'm fine inside.

541
00:27:58,200 --> 00:28:01,140
He needs to lie low and stay safe.

542
00:28:01,800 --> 00:28:04,060
Attorney Cheng Zijian promised

543
00:28:04,520 --> 00:28:06,140
I'll start serving time soon,

544
00:28:06,600 --> 00:28:07,980
earn merit, get a sentence cut,

545
00:28:08,560 --> 00:28:10,260
and we'll reunite early.

546
00:28:12,640 --> 00:28:14,740
Clear?

547
00:28:20,800 --> 00:28:21,580
Repeat it.

548
00:28:33,640 --> 00:28:35,100
Your dad says

549
00:28:36,280 --> 00:28:38,500
he's fine inside.

550
00:28:39,680 --> 00:28:40,900
He wants you

551
00:28:41,600 --> 00:28:44,420
to stay safe and behave.

552
00:28:45,160 --> 00:28:47,100
Attorney Cheng has guaranteed

553
00:28:47,920 --> 00:28:49,860
he'll start his term soon,

554
00:28:49,920 --> 00:28:51,220
win a reduction

555
00:28:51,240 --> 00:28:52,540
- and unite with the family early.
- Guard!

556
00:29:09,480 --> 00:29:10,040
Assistant Wang.

557
00:29:10,040 --> 00:29:21,160
[Director's Office
Haidong Provincial People's Procuratorate]

558
00:29:21,160 --> 00:29:21,660
Come in.

559
00:29:23,520 --> 00:29:24,480
Well, sir!

560
00:29:24,480 --> 00:29:25,240
[Sun Xiangqun
Director, Eleventh Division]

561
00:29:25,240 --> 00:29:26,500
Haven't seen you for two days.

562
00:29:26,520 --> 00:29:27,140
Where've you been?

563
00:29:27,480 --> 00:29:29,340
Do I have to file a report
every time I leave the office?

564
00:29:32,800 --> 00:29:34,300
Mission accomplished,

565
00:29:34,680 --> 00:29:35,820
the Wang Chunxiang case.

566
00:29:37,480 --> 00:29:38,020
Went smoothly?

567
00:29:38,320 --> 00:29:39,140
Smooth as silk.

568
00:29:44,080 --> 00:29:44,700
Then get back to work.

569
00:29:45,160 --> 00:29:45,980
What are you still doing here?

570
00:29:46,560 --> 00:29:47,300
Work?

571
00:29:48,080 --> 00:29:49,020
I've handed everything over.

572
00:29:49,240 --> 00:29:50,540
Nothing left.

573
00:29:50,960 --> 00:29:52,620
Trying to hurry me
into signing your exit papers, huh?

574
00:29:55,000 --> 00:29:56,500
You've been my boss for years.

575
00:29:56,760 --> 00:29:57,580
You know

576
00:29:57,760 --> 00:29:59,060
I'm no climber.

577
00:30:00,160 --> 00:30:01,380
Even if you

578
00:30:01,400 --> 00:30:03,180
never sign that resignation,

579
00:30:03,920 --> 00:30:05,060
you'll still be my good leader,

580
00:30:05,160 --> 00:30:06,140
my good friend.

581
00:30:06,720 --> 00:30:09,260
I've put your paperwork in.

582
00:30:09,840 --> 00:30:11,780
Prosecutor Zhang just started

583
00:30:12,040 --> 00:30:13,220
and he's buried.

584
00:30:13,520 --> 00:30:14,020
Give it a little time.

585
00:30:15,280 --> 00:30:16,780
That what a friend says?

586
00:30:17,360 --> 00:30:18,180
What,

587
00:30:19,880 --> 00:30:21,740
you want me to chase Zhang for you?

588
00:30:22,040 --> 00:30:23,820
Come on, don't mess with me.

589
00:30:23,840 --> 00:30:25,460
You know I'm eager to leave.

590
00:30:25,560 --> 00:30:26,500
Stop throwing roadblocks.

591
00:30:30,560 --> 00:30:31,020
Hong Liang,

592
00:30:31,800 --> 00:30:33,220
there are only two reasons

593
00:30:33,440 --> 00:30:34,580
someone can't wait to shed the uniform.

594
00:30:35,240 --> 00:30:36,700
One: they've gone slack,

595
00:30:37,200 --> 00:30:38,700
lost their ideals

596
00:30:38,840 --> 00:30:40,860
and passion for the work.

597
00:30:41,000 --> 00:30:41,820
Is that you?

598
00:30:42,080 --> 00:30:42,900
Definitely not.

599
00:30:43,560 --> 00:30:45,220
Two: they've got dirt

600
00:30:45,480 --> 00:30:46,380
that won't wash off.

601
00:30:48,320 --> 00:30:49,620
I'm squeaky clean.

602
00:30:50,160 --> 00:30:52,100
Would a shady guy even make it
into the Eleventh Division?

603
00:30:52,440 --> 00:30:53,620
Check eight generations.

604
00:30:53,640 --> 00:30:54,620
I'm as red-blooded as they come.

605
00:30:54,880 --> 00:30:56,220
Cleanest in the whole office.

606
00:30:56,600 --> 00:30:59,140
Exactly. Everyone in Eleventh is solid.

607
00:30:59,320 --> 00:31:01,380
And we see the bigger picture, right?

608
00:31:04,200 --> 00:31:05,260
Give me a bit of leave

609
00:31:05,560 --> 00:31:07,620
so I can calm my wife first.

610
00:31:07,680 --> 00:31:08,100
How many days?

611
00:31:08,720 --> 00:31:09,860
Come on, at least a month.

612
00:31:10,880 --> 00:31:12,300
Okay, 20 days.

613
00:31:13,000 --> 00:31:14,380
Fifteen is rock bottom.

614
00:31:14,400 --> 00:31:15,660
I can't spare a day less.

615
00:31:16,160 --> 00:31:16,620
You see,

616
00:31:17,880 --> 00:31:19,580
I've got to rent a place,

617
00:31:19,840 --> 00:31:22,300
find a school for the kid,

618
00:31:22,720 --> 00:31:24,740
schedule dinner

619
00:31:25,000 --> 00:31:26,940
with the new boss.

620
00:31:26,960 --> 00:31:28,780
Big shots aren't easy to book.

621
00:31:29,080 --> 00:31:30,580
I even had to go there myself each time,

622
00:31:30,680 --> 00:31:32,220
and the schedule was never fixed.

623
00:31:32,640 --> 00:31:34,340
I need some buffer.

624
00:31:34,400 --> 00:31:36,300
Seven days, public holidays included.

625
00:31:36,960 --> 00:31:37,940
You're a lawyer,

626
00:31:39,120 --> 00:31:40,500
cutting into statutory holidays?

627
00:31:40,960 --> 00:31:41,980
One day to find housing,

628
00:31:42,000 --> 00:31:43,380
one to hunt schools,

629
00:31:43,440 --> 00:31:44,220
one

630
00:31:44,440 --> 00:31:46,540
to wine-and-dine the new colleagues,

631
00:31:46,640 --> 00:31:48,340
the rest for the wife.

632
00:31:48,720 --> 00:31:51,340
Your minimum's three days

633
00:31:51,840 --> 00:31:52,980
but you ask for one month.

634
00:31:53,560 --> 00:31:54,100
How does that compute?

635
00:31:58,320 --> 00:32:00,220
Friends see through but don't call it out.

636
00:32:01,240 --> 00:32:01,980
Seven days will do.

637
00:32:02,480 --> 00:32:03,060
Deal.

638
00:32:04,240 --> 00:32:04,620
I'm off.

639
00:32:08,040 --> 00:32:08,580
Mr. Wang,

640
00:32:09,280 --> 00:32:09,860
listen to me.

641
00:32:10,480 --> 00:32:11,620
I'll brief the higher-ups

642
00:32:12,560 --> 00:32:13,540
and ask for a reinvestigation.

643
00:32:14,880 --> 00:32:16,500
Don't shoulder everything yourself.

644
00:32:17,200 --> 00:32:18,540
Those two bailiffs
bear some responsibility too.

645
00:32:19,080 --> 00:32:21,060
One person taking the fall versus three

646
00:32:21,560 --> 00:32:22,660
makes a big difference in discipline.

647
00:32:23,200 --> 00:32:23,780
No need.

648
00:32:24,880 --> 00:32:25,460
So you'd drag

649
00:32:26,960 --> 00:32:28,940
two brand-new bailiffs down with me?

650
00:32:29,520 --> 00:32:30,740
Those kids finally landed stable jobs.

651
00:32:31,440 --> 00:32:33,020
Do you have any idea

652
00:32:33,760 --> 00:32:35,060
how hard the civil-service exam is?

653
00:32:35,280 --> 00:32:36,180
And you have it easy?

654
00:32:36,880 --> 00:32:38,020
You're months from retirement.

655
00:32:38,520 --> 00:32:40,260
Once Hong Liang files today,

656
00:32:40,680 --> 00:32:41,780
your demotion

657
00:32:42,120 --> 00:32:43,260
is a done deal.

658
00:32:45,080 --> 00:32:46,740
Have you and Auntie calculated

659
00:32:47,120 --> 00:32:48,500
how much your pension will drop?

660
00:34:11,480 --> 00:34:11,940
Mr. Wang.

661
00:34:14,280 --> 00:34:15,340
How'd you even find this place?

662
00:34:16,000 --> 00:34:16,540
Asked around.

663
00:34:17,800 --> 00:34:18,860
Brought a few bottles of liquor for you.

664
00:34:20,760 --> 00:34:21,340
Then come in.

665
00:34:21,880 --> 00:34:22,780
Let me take it.

666
00:34:23,720 --> 00:34:24,260
Honey,

667
00:34:24,880 --> 00:34:25,620
we've got company!

668
00:34:25,960 --> 00:34:26,980
Oh, Auntie's home?

669
00:34:27,880 --> 00:34:28,340
Hello, Auntie.

670
00:34:29,000 --> 00:34:29,940
Here's some fruit.

671
00:34:30,520 --> 00:34:32,420
So you know he's been wronged?

672
00:34:33,400 --> 00:34:35,740
I'm really touched

673
00:34:36,280 --> 00:34:37,500
you all came to see him.

674
00:34:38,240 --> 00:34:39,260
- You are...
- You all?

675
00:34:47,800 --> 00:34:48,500
Just remembered

676
00:34:48,520 --> 00:34:49,460
a meeting at home.

677
00:34:49,640 --> 00:34:50,500
Gotta run.

678
00:34:51,400 --> 00:34:51,980
Don't go!

679
00:34:52,160 --> 00:34:52,860
No, the office...

680
00:34:52,880 --> 00:34:54,620
Since you're here, stay.

681
00:34:55,120 --> 00:34:55,420
Come on.

682
00:34:55,440 --> 00:34:55,780
Come inside.

683
00:34:55,800 --> 00:34:56,300
Hurry in.

684
00:34:56,520 --> 00:34:57,020
Dinner's ready.

685
00:34:57,040 --> 00:34:57,580
Really, I...

686
00:34:57,600 --> 00:34:58,260
Come on, come on.

687
00:34:58,280 --> 00:34:59,380
- Ms. Zheng, you're here too.
- Get inside.

688
00:34:59,440 --> 00:35:00,620
Right place, right time.

689
00:35:00,640 --> 00:35:01,660
- Yes.
- This way, quickly.

690
00:35:01,840 --> 00:35:02,300
- Come.
- I...

691
00:35:02,920 --> 00:35:03,260
No...

692
00:35:03,280 --> 00:35:04,140
Sit right here.

693
00:35:04,280 --> 00:35:05,140
Next to Yaping.

694
00:35:05,560 --> 00:35:06,460
I'll grab bowls and chopsticks.

695
00:35:07,440 --> 00:35:08,180
What luck.

696
00:35:08,880 --> 00:35:10,340
Nice liquor. Sauce-aroma baijiu.

697
00:35:10,400 --> 00:35:11,460
Let's drink this tonight.

698
00:35:11,960 --> 00:35:12,220
Great.

699
00:35:12,240 --> 00:35:13,300
I've brought the cups.

700
00:35:13,880 --> 00:35:15,540
Did you get this from your father-in-law

701
00:35:15,560 --> 00:35:16,900
or buy it yourself?

702
00:35:19,800 --> 00:35:21,220
Bought it myself, of course.

703
00:35:21,480 --> 00:35:22,900
Your father-in-law sells liquor?

704
00:35:24,280 --> 00:35:26,260
He used to be our boss.

705
00:35:26,960 --> 00:35:27,780
A leader?

706
00:35:28,560 --> 00:35:29,420
Retiring soon.

707
00:35:29,600 --> 00:35:30,820
Serves on the provincial CPPCC now.

708
00:35:30,840 --> 00:35:31,660
Still a leader.

709
00:35:32,400 --> 00:35:32,980
Aren't you hot?

710
00:35:33,360 --> 00:35:33,940
Take off your coat.

711
00:35:34,320 --> 00:35:34,780
Right, right.

712
00:35:36,600 --> 00:35:38,100
Just in time for dinner.

713
00:35:40,200 --> 00:35:41,980
I've been skipping supper,

714
00:35:42,200 --> 00:35:42,820
trying to slim down.

715
00:35:43,520 --> 00:35:45,500
Lost track of time.

716
00:35:46,000 --> 00:35:46,580
Sorry to barge in.

717
00:35:46,840 --> 00:35:48,180
Skipping dinner's no good.

718
00:35:48,400 --> 00:35:48,980
Bad for the stomach.

719
00:35:49,440 --> 00:35:50,460
These dumplings just came out.

720
00:35:50,600 --> 00:35:51,700
Try them while they're hot.

721
00:35:51,720 --> 00:35:52,300
All right.

722
00:35:52,800 --> 00:35:53,180
Here you are.

723
00:35:54,440 --> 00:35:54,940
None for me.

724
00:35:56,760 --> 00:35:57,140
Mr. Wang.

725
00:35:57,400 --> 00:35:57,860
Thank you, thank you.

726
00:35:57,880 --> 00:35:58,580
Look at this kid.

727
00:36:01,320 --> 00:36:02,260
Sorry, sorry, my fault.

728
00:36:03,960 --> 00:36:04,500
Here, give it to me.

729
00:36:05,080 --> 00:36:05,620
Auntie,

730
00:36:06,480 --> 00:36:07,500
let me introduce:

731
00:36:08,920 --> 00:36:09,420
this is Hong Liang,

732
00:36:10,400 --> 00:36:12,060
the Eleventh Division prosecutor

733
00:36:12,080 --> 00:36:13,380
handling Mr. Wang's case.

734
00:36:13,760 --> 00:36:14,260
Hong Liang.

735
00:36:21,240 --> 00:36:21,740
Auntie.

736
00:36:23,360 --> 00:36:24,700
She'll stir-fry two more dishes.

737
00:36:24,960 --> 00:36:25,660
Fry what?

738
00:36:25,880 --> 00:36:26,500
There's no food left.

739
00:36:37,760 --> 00:36:38,260
Hong,

740
00:36:40,280 --> 00:36:42,300
you're the prosecutor
of Eleventh Division,

741
00:36:43,000 --> 00:36:45,060
and the lead prosecutor on my case,

742
00:36:45,760 --> 00:36:46,180
yet

743
00:36:47,040 --> 00:36:48,020
you came to my house in person.

744
00:36:49,280 --> 00:36:50,380
I understand

745
00:36:50,840 --> 00:36:51,660
and appreciate it.

746
00:36:52,280 --> 00:36:53,900
I was the one at fault.

747
00:36:55,040 --> 00:36:56,100
You did nothing wrong.

748
00:37:01,720 --> 00:37:02,420
Working with

749
00:37:03,200 --> 00:37:04,100
Ms. Zheng lately,

750
00:37:04,720 --> 00:37:05,900
I've learned a lot.

751
00:37:06,600 --> 00:37:08,140
She's an outstanding prosecutor.

752
00:37:08,280 --> 00:37:08,580
Exactly.

753
00:37:09,080 --> 00:37:10,260
I hope you two

754
00:37:10,480 --> 00:37:11,460
become good friends.

755
00:37:11,800 --> 00:37:12,420
Sure.

756
00:37:13,040 --> 00:37:15,260
Preferably not just work contacts.

757
00:37:16,160 --> 00:37:16,660
Can't.

758
00:37:18,640 --> 00:37:19,660
He's leaving soon.

759
00:37:21,840 --> 00:37:22,780
I heard

760
00:37:23,840 --> 00:37:26,020
you're quitting because you didn't
get promoted to deputy director.

761
00:37:27,280 --> 00:37:28,660
Makes me sound power-hungry.

762
00:37:29,040 --> 00:37:29,540
Well, I am.

763
00:37:30,040 --> 00:37:30,420
No,

764
00:37:30,800 --> 00:37:32,700
you deserve that title.

765
00:37:32,720 --> 00:37:34,020
You're my role model.

766
00:37:35,920 --> 00:37:36,580
What year did you join?

767
00:37:37,280 --> 00:37:38,820
Twenty-ten...

768
00:37:38,840 --> 00:37:39,740
Older than me, right?

769
00:37:40,200 --> 00:37:40,500
Yeah.

770
00:37:40,640 --> 00:37:42,900
At your age, still no deputy director...

771
00:37:45,360 --> 00:37:45,780
Hong Liang,

772
00:37:47,920 --> 00:37:48,740
that liquor you brought

773
00:37:49,560 --> 00:37:49,940
is nice.

774
00:37:50,840 --> 00:37:51,860
Come on, let's drink.

775
00:37:52,080 --> 00:37:52,580
Sure.

776
00:37:53,840 --> 00:37:54,100
Cheers.

777
00:37:54,680 --> 00:37:55,100
Here's to you.

778
00:37:55,320 --> 00:37:55,660
Thanks.

779
00:38:02,160 --> 00:38:04,020
You said you're leaving. Where to?

780
00:38:05,520 --> 00:38:06,060
Beijing.

781
00:38:06,480 --> 00:38:07,140
The Supreme Procuratorate.

782
00:38:08,760 --> 00:38:09,740
Think they'll hand you

783
00:38:10,840 --> 00:38:12,420
a deputy-director post up there?

784
00:38:13,240 --> 00:38:15,460
I'm going to be general counsel,

785
00:38:15,800 --> 00:38:16,260
for a state-owned enterprise.

786
00:38:17,200 --> 00:38:17,660
A SOE, huh?

787
00:38:21,960 --> 00:38:22,540
Coat off.

788
00:38:23,880 --> 00:38:24,380
Hong,

789
00:38:24,760 --> 00:38:26,340
you're already a level-three senior.

790
00:38:27,560 --> 00:38:29,060
Can you really walk away
from the uniform?

791
00:38:30,160 --> 00:38:32,140
If he can be ruthless to his own,

792
00:38:32,680 --> 00:38:33,780
what's there to cling to?

793
00:38:36,960 --> 00:38:37,540
Mr. Wang,

794
00:38:38,920 --> 00:38:40,620
not everyone

795
00:38:41,680 --> 00:38:43,180
cherishes the uniform

796
00:38:43,880 --> 00:38:45,020
and honor the way you do.

797
00:38:45,040 --> 00:38:45,260
True.

798
00:38:45,280 --> 00:38:46,060
He values

799
00:38:46,840 --> 00:38:48,300
his honor most.

800
00:38:48,880 --> 00:38:50,980
He's been an
outstanding prosecutor every year.

801
00:38:51,080 --> 00:38:52,500
Slap a disciplinary mark on him,

802
00:38:52,640 --> 00:38:53,540
how can he

803
00:38:53,560 --> 00:38:55,420
- face his colleagues?
- Enough.

804
00:38:55,440 --> 00:38:56,580
Stop it.

805
00:38:56,920 --> 00:38:57,300
You...

806
00:39:01,560 --> 00:39:02,540
Ms. Zheng,

807
00:39:03,320 --> 00:39:03,860
shall we...

808
00:39:04,360 --> 00:39:05,020
Eat.

809
00:39:06,640 --> 00:39:07,620
How?

810
00:39:08,400 --> 00:39:09,380
While it's hot.

811
00:40:24,360 --> 00:40:24,940
Mr. Wang,

812
00:40:26,000 --> 00:40:27,140
do you know why

813
00:40:28,040 --> 00:40:29,100
I seconded you

814
00:40:29,120 --> 00:40:30,260
to help with this case?

815
00:40:32,560 --> 00:40:34,140
The first time I met you

816
00:40:34,280 --> 00:40:36,420
was at the Outstanding Prosecutors'
Commendation Ceremony.

817
00:40:36,880 --> 00:40:38,460
Over the years

818
00:40:39,440 --> 00:40:40,380
you've handled 2,183 cases,

819
00:40:40,400 --> 00:40:42,420
large and small,

820
00:40:42,720 --> 00:40:43,980
without a single slip-up.

821
00:40:44,880 --> 00:40:47,020
Even nationwide,

822
00:40:48,440 --> 00:40:50,260
that figure

823
00:40:50,280 --> 00:40:51,460
is astounding.

824
00:40:52,040 --> 00:40:53,420
A fair society

825
00:40:54,080 --> 00:40:55,060
depends on

826
00:40:55,680 --> 00:40:56,580
prosecutors like you.

827
00:40:56,960 --> 00:40:58,660
Ms. Zheng, since you said that,

828
00:40:58,680 --> 00:40:59,420
I have something to add,

829
00:40:59,440 --> 00:41:00,300
if I may.

830
00:41:00,360 --> 00:41:01,900
When I heard 2,183,

831
00:41:01,920 --> 00:41:02,900
- Prosecutor Hong,
- my mind just...

832
00:41:05,120 --> 00:41:06,780
may I ask you something?

833
00:41:08,320 --> 00:41:09,100
I'm all ears.

834
00:41:09,720 --> 00:41:10,580
What counts

835
00:41:10,600 --> 00:41:12,580
as outstanding

836
00:41:12,600 --> 00:41:13,260
in your Eleventh Division?

837
00:41:13,640 --> 00:41:14,820
Our Commissioner Sun defines it as...

838
00:41:14,840 --> 00:41:16,300
How many of your own people

839
00:41:18,440 --> 00:41:20,140
do you have to take down
to hit your annual KPIs?

840
00:41:30,000 --> 00:41:30,980
Maybe I'm thinking too small.

841
00:41:33,240 --> 00:41:33,700
Put it this way:

842
00:41:35,080 --> 00:41:36,700
what sort of case

843
00:41:38,640 --> 00:41:39,340
earns you a citation?

844
00:41:55,400 --> 00:41:56,100
If we're talking citations,

845
00:41:56,600 --> 00:41:58,540
my husband just got the biggest one.

846
00:41:59,120 --> 00:42:00,860
Is this how you treat someone
who's done the system a favor?

847
00:42:01,120 --> 00:42:02,700
Do you even have a conscience?

848
00:42:03,040 --> 00:42:04,300
That's enough!

849
00:42:06,480 --> 00:42:07,060
You realize

850
00:42:07,880 --> 00:42:09,260
if Lin Xi really dies,

851
00:42:09,600 --> 00:42:10,900
I won't even be able to go home,

852
00:42:11,960 --> 00:42:13,700
let alone sit here eating dumplings.

853
00:42:50,080 --> 00:42:56,880
[Yongqing River, Dongping City]

854
00:43:16,240 --> 00:43:20,240
At the river's end,
bitter rain and brutal waves

855
00:43:20,240 --> 00:43:23,880
A human life is strewn with hardship

856
00:43:23,880 --> 00:43:27,680
Brother, there's a weight on my heart

857
00:43:27,680 --> 00:43:31,560
Until I meet Old Lady Meng,
I can't let it go

858
00:43:31,560 --> 00:43:35,280
Since ancient days,
black and white have stood apart

859
00:43:35,280 --> 00:43:38,920
Don't preach
that letting go makes you a Buddha

860
00:43:38,920 --> 00:43:42,560
Even good folk may die unrewarded

861
00:43:42,560 --> 00:43:47,200
So why should the wicked live in ease?

862
00:43:47,200 --> 00:43:54,560
For one last breath,
for one clear principle

863
00:43:54,560 --> 00:44:02,240
For this single rite,
I'll see it through to the end

864
00:44:02,240 --> 00:44:10,360
I will wear my life thin
just to glimpse the snow-orchid bloom

865
00:44:10,360 --> 00:44:17,760
I will shred these shoes
and barefoot tame the wind-blown sands

866
00:44:17,760 --> 00:44:25,360
I will face rosy clouds by day
and lift a torch by night

867
00:44:25,360 --> 00:44:32,440
Beneath the bright firmament,
I want every deed bound by law

868
00:44:32,440 --> 00:44:40,200
I want the ones who set out
to return home, no matter how late

869
00:44:40,200 --> 00:44:47,840
I want the rain that falls from heaven
to rise back into heaven

870
00:44:47,840 --> 00:44:55,040
I want to earn my daily bread
while guarding this wild land

871
00:44:55,040 --> 00:45:02,440
I want every righteous path on earth
to stand beneath clear skies

872
00:45:02,440 --> 00:45:10,200
I want the well-diggers' pockets
lined with salt

873
00:45:10,200 --> 00:45:18,080
And I want the heartless cheats
to feel the justice in their eyes
